headline: First Watch Restaurant Group, Inc. (FWRG) Lags Q4 Earnings Estimates
summary: First Watch Restaurant Group (FWRG) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of -50% and 0.43%, respectively, for the quarter ended December 2024. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
